review.reviewBody: pizza came luke warm. borderline cold. $32 for $30 wings? dont even get me started on the size of these wings. literally half the size of my index finger. pathetic

The food is good but I dont get a option for flavour on Combo 6 (Medium Specialty Pizza) or any combo I tried to talk to the manager but he told me to call doordash my self so they can charge extra on the order but when i called they said he had to change it????
really bad pizza. dough was absolutely garbage
I called for the flavor for the wings and they came over cooked and no sauce this never happens very disappointing
